Package: AbunRNA
Type: Package
Title: An R package For Expression Abundance Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("ChengYue", "Zhang", 
                  email = "shengyue.zhang@mail.utoronto.ca", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: ChengYue Zhang <shengyue.zhang@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: Performs analysis on transcript expression abundance. Pipeline 
    includes downloading Miniconda, creating conda environment to download
    Salmon software for indexing and quantification, generating count matrix
    for input sequences, plot heatmap to visualize abundance difference among
    wild type and mutant types, and perform principle component analysis to
    obtain more explainatory results.
